Package: LibeRary
Title: Pharmacometric Model Repository for the LibeR Ecosystem
Version: 0.7.5
Authors@R:
    person("Sven C.", "van Dijkman", email = "svdijkman@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Searchable, versioned pharmacometric model repository and literature
    ingestion workflow for the LibeR ecosystem. Discovers publications, acquires
    full text, extracts and independently reconciles model evidence with
    user-selectable local or remote language models, retains auditable provenance,
    and imports NONMEM-style models into LibeRation workspaces.
